OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy overnight, with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain affecting western hills, while
OL,8,Fareas further east are likely to
OL,9,Fremain largely dry. Breezy throughout
OL,10,Fthe night and feeling mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA slow-moving band of rain
OL,13,Fwill gradually move eastwards across
OL,14,Fall parts on Monday morning,
OL,15,Ffragmenting as it does so, with
OL,16,Fperhaps a few brighter spells late
OL,17,Fafternoon. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
