OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FAfter
OL,6,Fa chilly start, Tuesday will be dry
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells and light winds.
OL,8,FSimilar conditions Wednesday.
OL,9,FRemaining dry with sunny spells
OL,10,FThursday. Temperatures generally a
OL,11,Flittle above the average.
